  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective, multicenter, non-randomized study to determine the performance of NUVANT Mobile
      Cardiac Telemetry system in arrhythmia detection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Arrhythmia patients will be externally monitored. The collected information will be used to
      evaluate the NUVANT MCT system.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
